	<li>Tekkie Town is seeking to employ a Creditors Controller (overheads) for a 10 month contract. The successful candidate will be responsible for processing of supplier invoices, reconciling supplier statements, following up on credit notes or discrepancies (price and quantity differences) and preparing payments and submitting remittance advice.</li>
